== Welcome to RubyReview
Ruby on Rails implementation of an employee review application

== Getting Started
1. Following instructions on how to install Ruby, Gem, and Rails at http://rubyonrails.org/download
2. Install sqlite (gem install sqlite3)
   * Download sqlite binaries (http://www.sqlite.org/sqlitedll-3_7_3.zip) to your Ruby bin directory (ex: C:\Ruby\bin)
3. Build db (rake db:migrate)
6. Open in editor of your choice!

